{"tid":2204283,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"人地富東閣300元包車送貨 渣哥班友用自己車送 抽油水抽到逐碟收30元行政費係咩玩法？","createTime":"2020-09-16T03:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T05:07:32.000Z","uid":252492,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6357b3938c16ccf12685ceaf8bad74a1574f611","tid":2204283,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nATHtin.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnATHtin.png&h=968b170c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果醬便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「幾千不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;幾千！&hellip;&hellip;幾千蚊的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「自食其力」，什麼「龍粉」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</blockquote>好撚顛係咁屌太古街坊窮閪<br />\n仆街人地酒樓有平價車隊送<br />\n你水人加幾十元隻找你送喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔係水人加幾十蚊<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">根據琴日睇太古人個page cap圖係<br />\n每樣野$30運費 即係片皮鴨$30 叫隻雞$30 炒碟菜$30 <br />\n片皮鴨個二食$10 <br />\n即係咁樣叫要俾$100運費</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於酒樓本來個運費係 全部order 裝得上酒樓架車既都係$300包車<br />\n總之你愈多人叫 咪愈平 因為平均分擔個$300</blockquote>仆街 逐樣計 咁大生意都比佢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7eb9e7d5953b21fe88964795c3ae1d6162cefb","tid":2204283,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289a1b48b101eef45bf346c3dde6002345022a3c","tid":2204283,"uid":60279,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"分分鐘係用酒樓車 再話自己送既 <br />\n前後油錢時間都唔洗比"},{"pid":"d75c3bbf531fa0582d8829f6ae8096fa8c203b59","tid":2204283,"uid":80178,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"黃圈都幾多賤種下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c1d265a5b3ba5fdd60c7ef0c4e87a6747400c0","tid":2204283,"uid":144541,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote"